  "instructions": [
    "heat 1 teaspoon of mustard oil in a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "add sliced onion and saut for 3 minutes until translucent.",
    "add minced garlic and saut for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "add sliced red peppers and saut for 3 minutes until tender.",
    "add ground turmeric, cumin, and cayenne pepper. stir well to combine.",
    "add salt and stir well to combine.",
    "add 1 tablespoon of butter and stir well to combine.",
    "garnish with chopped cilantro and a sprinkle of ras el hanout.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!"
